<!-- 定義及症狀 -->
'''過敏性鼻炎'''，又稱為'''鼻敏感'''、'''乾草熱'''、'''花粉熱'''、'''花粉症'''或'''季節性過敏性鼻炎'''，是因為[[免疫系統|免疫系統]]受到空氣中的[[過敏原|過敏原]]影響而導致的[[鼻炎|鼻炎]]症狀<ref name=NIH2015Imm>{{cite web|title=Immunotherapy for Environmental Allergies|url=http://www.niaid.nih.gov/topics/environmental-allergies/Pages/immunotherapy.aspx|website=NIAID|accessdate=19 June 2015|date=May 12, 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150617190743/http://www.niaid.nih.gov/topics/environmental-allergies/Pages/immunotherapy.aspx|archivedate=2015-06-17}}</ref>。徵兆和病症包括流鼻涕或鼻塞、[[打噴嚏|打噴嚏]]、眼睛的紅癢與溢淚、眼睛周圍腫脹<ref>{{cite web|title=Environmental Allergies: Symptoms|url=http://www.niaid.nih.gov/topics/environmental-allergies/Pages/symptoms.aspx|website=NIAID|accessdate=19 June 2015|date=April 22, 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150618023408/http://www.niaid.nih.gov/topics/environmental-allergies/Pages/symptoms.aspx|archivedate=2015-06-18}}</ref><ref name=NIH2015Sym>{{cite web|title=Environmental Allergies: Symptoms|url=http://www.niaid.nih.gov/topics/environmental-allergies/Pages/symptoms.aspx|website=NIAID|accessdate=19 June 2015|date=April 22, 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150618023408/http://www.niaid.nih.gov/topics/environmental-allergies/Pages/symptoms.aspx|archivedate=18 June 2015|df=}}</ref> 。從鼻腔流出的液體通常是清澈的<!-- <ref name=NEJM2015/> -->。症狀通常會在接觸過敏原後的幾分鐘後產生，而且會影響睡眠、工作能力以及在學習時的注意力<ref name=NEJM2015/>，因為花粉而有病徵的患者，大概都集中在一年的特定時間發病<ref name=NIH2015Cause/>。許多過敏性鼻炎的病患也會為[[氣喘|氣喘]]、[[過敏性結膜炎|過敏性結膜炎]]或[[異位性皮膚炎|異位性皮膚炎]]所苦<ref name=NEJM2015>{{cite journal|last1=Wheatley|first1=LM|last2=Togias|first2=A|title=Clinical practice. Allergic rhinitis.|journal=The New England journal of medicine|date=29 January 2015|volume=372|issue=5|pages=456-63|pmid=25629743}}</ref>。

<!-- 成因、機制及診斷 -->
過敏性鼻炎基本上是受到環境過敏原的誘發，例如花粉、動物毛髮、灰塵或黴菌<!-- <ref name=NIH2015Cause/> -->，遺傳[[基因|基因]]還有環境暴露都是造成過敏的原因<ref name=NIH2015Cause>{{cite web|title=Cause of Environmental Allergies|url=http://www.niaid.nih.gov/topics/environmental-allergies/Pages/cause.aspx|website=NIAID|accessdate=17 June 2015|date=April 22, 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150617124141/http://www.niaid.nih.gov/topics/environmental-allergies/Pages/cause.aspx|archivedate=2015-06-17}}</ref>。在農場裡長大或有多個兄弟姊妹都能減低罹患過敏的機率，<!-- <ref name=NEJM2015/> -->其作用機制和[[IgE抗體|IgE抗體]]有關，當此抗體接觸到過敏原時會促使[[肥大細胞|肥大細胞]]釋出像是[[組織胺|組織胺]]的化學物質來造成發炎反應<ref name=NEJM2015/>。診斷方法常仰賴[[病史|醫療病史]]，且結合{{le|皮膚過敏試驗|Skin allergy test}}或是抽血來檢查是否含有特定IgE抗體<!-- <ref name=NIH2015Diag/> -->。不過這些測試有時會呈現偽陽性<ref name=NIH2015Diag>{{cite web|title=Environmental Allergies: Diagnosis|url=http://www.niaid.nih.gov/topics/environmental-allergies/Pages/diagnosis.aspx|website=NIAID|accessdate=19 June 2015|date=May 12, 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150617185846/http://www.niaid.nih.gov/topics/environmental-allergies/Pages/diagnosis.aspx|archivedate=2015-06-17}}</ref>。過敏的病徵和[[普通感冒|普通感冒]]的症狀類似，但過敏的症狀常持續超過兩個禮拜而且較少會有[[發燒|發燒]]的情形<ref name=NIH2015Cause/>。

<!-- 預防及治療 -->
如果在幼童時期就開始接觸動物，則有機會降低日後因此而過敏的機會<ref name=NIH2015Cause/>。有部分藥物可以改善過敏症狀，當中包括鼻炎[[類固醇|類固醇]]、[[抗組織胺|抗組織胺]]，例如[[苯海拉明|苯海拉明]]、{{le|色甘酸|Cromoglicic acid|色甘酸鈉}}以及{{le|白三烯受體拮抗劑|Antileukotriene}}類的montelukast（藥品名：欣流）都屬此類<ref>{{cite web|title=Environmental Allergies: Treatments|url=http://www.niaid.nih.gov/topics/environmental-allergies/Pages/treatments.aspx|website=NIAID|accessdate=17 June 2015|date=April 22, 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150617164725/http://www.niaid.nih.gov/topics/environmental-allergies/Pages/treatments.aspx|archivedate=2015-06-17}}</ref><ref name=NIH2015Tx>{{cite web|title=Environmental Allergies: Treatments|url=http://www.niaid.nih.gov/topics/environmental-allergies/Pages/treatments.aspx|website=NIAID|accessdate=17 June 2015|date=April 22, 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150617164725/http://www.niaid.nih.gov/topics/environmental-allergies/Pages/treatments.aspx|archivedate=17 June 2015|df=}}</ref>。不過對許多人而言，藥物改善的效果有限，或是會有副作用<ref name=NEJM2015/>。{{le|過敏原免疫療法|allergen immunotherapy}}是讓人暴露在越來越多的過敏原中，此療法一般而言是有效的<!-- <ref name=NIH2015Imm/> -->，過敏原可以注射到體中，或是用口含錠的方式含在舌下<!-- <ref name=NIH2015Imm/> -->。<!--Treatment typically lasts three to five years after which benefits may be prolonged.<ref name=NIH2015Imm/>-->

<!-- 流行病學及歷史 -->
過敏性鼻炎是[[過敏|過敏]]的一種，會影響許多人的生活<ref name=Fire2002/>。西方國家在一年內約有10-30%的人們受過敏困擾<ref name=Dy2010>{{cite journal |vauthors =Dykewicz MS, Hamilos DL |title=Rhinitis and sinusitis |journal=The Journal of Allergy and Clinical Immunology |volume=125 |issue=2 Suppl 2 |pages=S103–15 |date=February 2010 |pmid=20176255 |doi=10.1016/j.jaci.2009.12.989 |url=}}</ref> <ref>{{cite journal |author=Dykewicz MS, Hamilos DL |title=Rhinitis and sinusitis |journal=The Journal of Allergy and Clinical Immunology |volume=125 |issue=2 Suppl 2 |pages=S103–15 |date=February 2010 |pmid=20176255 |doi=10.1016/j.jaci.2009.12.989 |url=|last2=Hamilos }}</ref><ref name=NEJM2015/>，最常見的年齡大概是從20-40歲左右<ref name=NEJM2015/>。在西元十世紀的時候，[[拉澤斯|拉澤斯]]醫師第一次對過敏有完整的敘述<ref>{{cite book|last1=Colgan|first1=Richard|title=Advice to the young physician on the art of medicine|date=2009|publisher=Springer|location=New York|isbn=9781441910349|page=31|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=DoMVs4HuDAoC&pg=PA31|access-date=2016-03-18|archive-date=2019-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190607222903/https://books.google.ca/books?id=DoMVs4HuDAoC&pg=PA31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1859年，{{le|查理·布萊克利|Charles Blackley}}醫師發現花粉是造成過敏的原因<ref name=BBC2014>{{cite news|author1=Justin Parkinson|title=John Bostock: The man who 'discovered' hay fever|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/magazine-28038630|accessdate=19 June 2015|publisher=BBC News Magazine|date=1 July 2014|archive-date=2018-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180615220559/https://www.bbc.com/news/magazine-28038630|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而{{le|皮奎特|Clemens von Pirque}}<ref name=Fire2002>{{cite book|last1=Fireman|first1=Philip|title=Pediatric otolaryngology vol 2.|date=2002|publisher=W. B. Saunders|location=Philadelphia, Pa.|isbn=9789997619846|page=1065|edition=4|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=y5rpEdeKtJEC&pg=PA1065|access-date=2016-03-18|archive-date=2020-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200203141300/https://books.google.ca/books?id=y5rpEdeKtJEC&pg=PA1065|dead-url=no}}</ref>和[[乾草|乾草]]的關聯卻是因為早期（且錯誤）的理論，該理論提到過敏其實是新乾草的味道引起的<ref name="Lancet1838">{{cite journal|title=Dr. Marshall Hall on Diseases of the Respiratory System; III. Hay Asthma|journal=The Lancet|date=May 19, 1838|page=245|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=OBVAAAAAcAAJ&pg=PA245|quote=With respect to what is termed the exciting cause of the disease, since the attention of the public has been turned to the subject an idea has very generally prevailed, that it is produced by the effluvium from new hay, and it has hence obtained the popular name of hay fever. [...] the effluvium from hay has no connection with the disease.|access-date=2016-03-18|archive-date=2020-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200203141255/https://books.google.ca/books?id=OBVAAAAAcAAJ&pg=PA245|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|title=History of Allergy|date=2014|publisher=Karger Medical and Scientific Publishers|isbn=9783318021950|page=62|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=dffSAwAAQBAJ&pg=PA62|access-date=2016-03-18|archive-date=2019-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190610141508/https://books.google.ca/books?id=dffSAwAAQBAJ&pg=PA62|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 症狀 ==
其症狀與[[感冒|感冒]]相似，主要且最大宗症狀為打[[噴嚏|噴嚏]]，其次也有[[眼睛|眼睛]]瘙[[癢|癢]]、鼻部癢、[[鼻塞|鼻塞]]、流[[鼻涕|鼻涕]]和流清水狀白色鼻涕（流鼻水）等症，間歇性反覆發作。發作時鼻黏膜蒼白水腫，如還有過敏體質會引起[[蕁麻疹|蕁麻疹]]。嚴重也有可能會演變成[[鼻竇炎|鼻竇炎]]、[[哮喘|哮喘]]或耳部感染。

